### Nosc Clinic Scheduling System — REST Client Requests
### Target Tenant: 42 (Nosc Clinic Berlin)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@tenantId = 42

### 1. Get Tenant Details & Timezone
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 2. Get Services List
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 3. Get Doctors List
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 4. Get Patients List
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 5. Search Availability (Service 7 - Advanced Ultrasound)
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability?serviceId=7&from=2026-10-15T00:00:00%2B02:00&to=2026-10-16T00:00:00%2B02:00&doctorIds=101,102
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 6. Create Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 555,
  "doctorId": 101,
  "roomId": 12,
  "serviceId": 7,
  "startsAt": "2026-10-15T08:05:00+02:00"
}

### 7. Get Doctor Schedule (Doctor 101)
GET {{baseUrl}}/doctors/101/schedule?from=2026-10-15T00:00:00%2B02:00&to=2026-10-16T00:00:00%2B02:00
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 8. Cancel Appointment (Replace 1 with created ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appointments/1
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
